borednomore3 (0.7.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Release.
  * Dynamic wallpaper changer with 1000+ ImageMagick transitions
  * Universal desktop environment support (GNOME, KDE, XFCE, LXQt, MATE, etc.)
  * Professional CustomTkinter GUI frontend (borednomore3-gui)
  * Command-line backend daemon (borednomore3)
  * Wallpaper downloader utility (borednomore3-downloader)
  * Modular Python library structure (libs/config, core, desktop, utils)
  * True random shuffle with playlist system (no repeats until full cycle)
  * Configuration file support with CLI override
  * Real-time debug mode
  * Man pages and desktop integration
  * Automatic desktop environment detection
  * Smart resolution detection via xrandr

 -- Nepamuceno Bartolo <packager@example.com>  Tue, 28 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
